{"tid":1128701,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺avengers好鐘意亂用激光","createTime":"2019-04-28T04:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T12:24:51.000Z","uid":7109,"like":9,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f0bd94b6aa201b1e64c68784bde021bb16fd7c66","tid":1128701,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"Tony發明iron man suit之後，早期至中期嘅激光係幾洗得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如: <br />\n佢射9個boss (iron man 1)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vt7Dz7T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVt7Dz7T.png&h=f1d0da6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同war machine一齊射爆boss ( iron man 2)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvzFOs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvzFOs1.png&h=92cec467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時候會亂用一下，例如同WM互射 (iron man 2)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRJvreY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRJvreY.png&h=019cf017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者用400%電力炸落去thor到，人地都只係反一反身就打返轉頭<br />\n你就反省下下下用激光掂唔掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hi0d8tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHi0d8tr.png&h=1f9f90f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9421Os.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9421Os.png&h=e101b575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到avengers 2，激光又work返<br />\n包括同vision and Thor 一齊射Ultron <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTWwU8N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTWwU8N.png&h=80570b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋同thor合作炸城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fJWmOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fJWmOZ.png&h=bf248d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知去到CA3，激光就玩臭咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVision承襲tony嘅戰術，用粒mind stone 射射<br />\n點知殺紅了眼，射到人半身不遂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDKOcVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDKOcVN.png&h=ecddc497&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/115858_837ad14918761fad8d13610bed112acb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F115858_837ad14918761fad8d13610bed112acb.png&h=24da2de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/115901_262070caf278691c98672c59f69c5abd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F115901_262070caf278691c98672c59f69c5abd.png&h=f1a584ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到avengers 3，又係用激光<br />\n結果仲俾人反傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjCgmPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjCgmPr.png&h=6a1f14ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPnstur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPnstur.png&h=a34b2c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVision 哥哥，射到咁上下耐就好停啦<br />\n<br />\nTony 一開場用激光打隻大隻佬係ok的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wurtcWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwurtcWc.png&h=f457605a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最後tony同thanos隻抽隻<br />\nTony又係用激光死射爛射<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMFqe9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMFqe9Y.png&h=42e79ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ma7Hhoj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fma7Hhoj.png&h=cc9ad1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大佬呀，射到咁上下好停啦，轉下手啦<br />\n<br />\nWanda用激光爆石同拖住thanos唔計<br />\n<br />\n結論: 唔亂用激光就唔洗死"},{"pid":"e2989d2c2079475e761e8e6b74c751df8fd7cc4b","tid":1128701,"uid":7109,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwyjjCr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwyjjCr.png&h=3fc15bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6WtcXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6WtcXs.png&h=630529da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8f51e03ba07841effb51abdf35c9d4076a5fca2","tid":1128701,"uid":16061,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔通用子彈"},{"pid":"30a24f4020243682fdbd05f11f2473fcb69f17b8","tid":1128701,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:20:53.000Z","msg":"cm 直頭日本啲超人咁𨶙樣"},{"pid":"8ce407d8bfa6dd8b145c914ae215baf06953642d","tid":1128701,"uid":25601,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"除左激光 你覺得佢拳腳有力？"},{"pid":"e5c57f7bfd80962f6ae894e6c3e571130e6cc8fd","tid":1128701,"uid":177924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"其實一直有個疑問<br />\n佢個激光威力到底係幾高<br />\nIronman3射人射唔穿<br />\nAvengers 2射得穿啲機械人"},{"pid":"e62d62dd28b93a5400e6d25f1a3ee40315850e0e","tid":1128701,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5c57f7bfd80962f6ae894e6c3e571130e6cc8fd","tid":1128701,"uid":177924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"其實一直有個疑問<br />\n佢個激光威力到底係幾高<br />\nIronman3射人射唔穿<br />\nAvengers 2射得穿啲機械人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"Bug嚟囉"},{"pid":"2231553559aaa6105d242a6b2561ce903ed9e97b","tid":1128701,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c57f7bfd80962f6ae894e6c3e571130e6cc8fd","tid":1128701,"uid":177924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"其實一直有個疑問<br />\n佢個激光威力到底係幾高<br />\nIronman3射人射唔穿<br />\nAvengers 2射得穿啲機械人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:43